Text: Thax a lot for all the cool stuff u r uploadin.It means a lot,really appreciate that.All these records,Y&T,Elegy,Zinatra,Sleeze Beez and all the rest uploaded,Dutch or not,have been part of my growing up,lots of memories...Left all of them,all my precious vynils,back at my parents home.Now,here where I live,in your same country I guess,I really needed this mp3 injection;)
